Class AbstractQuery

java.lang.Object
  ch.ethz.inf.vs.persistingservice.resources.persisting.history.time.AbstractQuery

public abstract class AbstractQuery
extends java.lang.Object

The Class AbstractQuery is a container for the method perform, which retrieves data from the database.

The abstract query is used to simulate method passing in Java.
